      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Dietrich Kappe</b>\n</p><p><b>Dietrich Kappe</b>,<br />\nan American computer expert, CTO of Orthogonal (a medical device software development and design company)<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. He is also an amateur blues musician, chess player, and political analyst.\n</p><p>He is the author of <a href=\"/A0lite\" title=\"A0lite\">A0lite</a>, a didactic <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">neural network</a> chess engine, written in <a href=\"/Python\" title=\"Python\">Python</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:DietrichKappe.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/DietrichKappe.jpg/300px-DietrichKappe.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/2/28/DietrichKappe.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:DietrichKappe.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Dietrich Kappe</div></div></div> \n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dietrich_Kappe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dietrich_Kappe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68789\">Leela Lite: A toolkit for experimenting with leela nets in python</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  October 31, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71171\">An opponent for humans: Bad Gyal</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 02, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72723\">Mean Girl 8 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 04, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73495\">New engine: a0lite</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 28, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=74837\">Night Nurse 0.2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Igel\" title=\"Igel\">Igel</a>, <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dietrich_Kappe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76787\">Re: Your motivation for writing a chess engine?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, Mar 06, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=80238\">Stockfish vs ChessBase hearing a “meh” affair</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, Jul 05, 2022</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dietrich_Kappe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/dkappe\">Dietrich Kappe GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dietrich_Kappe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">[<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://orthogonal.io/\">https://orthogonal.io/</a> Orthogonal</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301100923\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 37/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 74/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:8019-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301100923 and revision id 26503\n -->\n"
